						<div class="postbody">Essentially, I was attempting a subroutine to handle screen changes (different name tables).  The idea was to have a variable to determine what 'next screen' to draw.  So if I was at SCREEN00, i could change the variable to SCREEN01 (and if at SCREEN01, change it to SCREEN02, etc etc etc) so when that condition was met again, it would jump to the subroutine and load whatever nametable was pointed to through the variable, and then update the variable.<br /><br />Does that make more sense?</div>

